         <head type="date">
            <date>August 7, 1804</date>
         </head>
         <div type="entry">
            <sp who="wc">
               <speaker>Clark</speaker>
               <ab>
                  <date/>
               </ab>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="italic">August 7th Tuesday</hi>    last night about 8 oClock a Storm of wind from the N. W. which lasted ¾ of an hour    mosquitors more troublesom last night than I ever Saw them, Set out late this morning    wind N.</p>
